archimate:ApplicationComponent.name: EudraLink
archimate:ApplicationComponent.documentation: Eudralink is the European medicines regulatory networksecure file-transfer system used for exchanging information for regulatory purposes. A secure message transfer application for communication between EMEA, EU Member State drug regulatory agencies and the industry. Hosted by the EMEA and reachable via https://eudralink.emea.europa.eu/. Requires prior registration of applicants.
